docs {
  # Delete Disease
  
  Deletes a disease from the local database by its name.
  
  ## Request Body
  
  The body must contain the `name` field.
  
  ### Request Structure
  
  - `name` (string, required): The name of the disease to delete (case-insensitive)
    - Example: `"diabetes"`, `"Diabetes"`, or `"DIABETES"` all work
  
  ## Success Response (200 OK)
  
  ```json
  {
    "status": "success",
    "message": "Disease deleted successfully",
    "data": null
  }
  ```
  
  ## Error Response (404 Not Found)
  
  ```json
  {
    "status": "error",
    "message": "Disease not found"
  }
  ```
  
  ## Error Response (422 Validation Error)
  
  ```json
  {
    "status": "error",
    "message": "Validation Error: ✖ Required → at name",
    "errors": {
      "name": ["Required"]
    }
  }
  ```
}
